IMAPAccount sixsupersonic-gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User sixsupersonic@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass mbsync-sixsupersonic"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore sixsupersonic-gmail-remote
Account sixsupersonic-gmail

MaildirStore sixsupersonic-gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/sixsupersonic-gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/sixsupersonic-gmail/Inbox

Channel sixsupersonic-gmail
Far :sixsupersonic-gmail-remote:
Near :sixsupersonic-gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
SyncState *

